TODAY'S QUOTE 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
"How loud must we cry? How many of our children must die before our city 
leaders will say enough is enough and put an end to this suffering?" 
</P>
<P>
 -- Pat Moore, one of about 100 people who marched through the streets of 
Compton to demand an end to gang violence, such as the shooting that took the 
life of 2-year-old Phillip Fisher last month. 
</P>
