ruefully says: "I'm convinced we've reached the end of the gymnastics era in 
the L. A. schools." ; Photo, Sasvary, 55, who served as an Olympic judge in the 
1972 and 1984 Summer Games, examines the form of Adam Campbell. DAVID BUTOW / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
