CONSERVATIVES KEEP POWER IN BERMUNDA 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<BYLINE>
<P>
From Reuters 
</P>
</BYLINE>
<DATELINE>
<P>
HAMILTON, Bermuda 
</P>
