<P>
FUNERAL SERVICES SET FOR TEACHER HIT BY CAR 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Funeral services will be held Saturday for Don Hendricks, a Fullerton College 
art teacher killed when he was struck by a car as he rode his bike to school. 
</P>
<P>
Services for the popular instructor and renowned watercolor painter will be 
held at 2 p.m. at the Church of Jesus Christ of Latter-day Saints, 2225 N. 
Euclid Ave. in Fullerton. 
</P>
<P>
In lieu of flowers, the Hendricks family has asked that memorial donations be 
sent to: The Fullerton College Foundation Memorial Scholarship Fund, Fullerton 
College, 321 E. Chapman Ave., Fullerton, Calif. 92634. 
</P>
